@@TJvLogFile.Add@string
Description:
Use this method to add an entry to the log. This method has only a unique parameter, the title of the event. The time is automatically inserted (the time used is the current time).

Parameters:
Title: 
is the title of the event to add in the log

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvLogFile.Add@string@string@string
Description:
Use this method to add an entry to the log. The time should be the current time, but you can enter anything you want, and use the format you want.

Parameters:
Time: 
is the time of the event.
Title: 
is the title of the event to add in the log
Description: 
is the description of the event

