@@TLogRecord
Description:
This class is used to retrieve information from a log file. This class is used in the TJvLogFile component.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TLogRecord.Description
Description:
This variable contains the text message associated with the current entry.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TLogRecord.Time
Description:
This variable contains the time of the current record. The time may be in any format (The value is the same you have specified when adding an entry)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TLogRecord.Title
Description:
This variable contains the title of the current record. This is a generic title for the entry (ex: ERROR, STATUS, ...).

